      <h1 class="blog-title">Power Flushing Central Heating: The Complete Liverpool Guide. Costs, Signs and What Really Happens.</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Cold radiators, a noisy boiler, heating that gets worse every winter. Sludge is usually the culprit. Here is everything Liverpool homeowners need to know before spending a penny.</p>
